When I add new page in web editor with name "JIT007aWebPageb" & slug "/JIT007aWebPageb/slug"
Then I should see the page in web editor with name "JIT007aWebPageb" & slug "/JIT007aWebPageb/slug" display in list "Pages"
When I select screen with name JIT007aWebPagea
When I select tab list with name "Layers"
When I open Search popup on item value "Box" with index "1"
When I add item "Image" in Search popup with sub menu "Basic" to preview mobile editor
When I select item value "Image" with index "1"
When I select dropdown field label "Image Type" of header "Image" with value "Upload"
When I open image asset manager for field label "Image Type" of header "Image" without active image
Then I should see Asset Manager panel display
When I upload image in Asset Manager with path "/assets/images/img1.png"
Then I should see image asset item with name "img1" display
When I upload image in Asset Manager with path "/assets/images/img2.jpeg"
Then I should see image asset item with name "img2" display
Then I should see image asset item list match with baseline title "WEB.JIT007.Asset.ListItem.Img1Img2" with threshold "1"
When I select image name "img1" in Asset Manager panel
Then I should see the preview web editor match with baseline title "WEB.JIT007.Asset.Img1" for the threshold "1"
When I select image name "img2" in Asset Manager panel
Then I should see the preview web editor match with baseline title "WEB.JIT007.Asset.Img2" for the threshold "1"
When I close Asset Manager panel
When I select tab list with name "Pages"
When I select tab name Pages with index 1
When I select screen with name JIT007aWebPageb
When I select tab list with name "Layers"
When I open Search popup on item value "Box" with index "1"
When I add item "Image" in Search popup with sub menu "Basic" to preview mobile editor
When I select item value "Image" with index "1"
When I select dropdown field label "Image Type" of header "Image" with value "Upload"
When I open image asset manager for field label "Image Type" of header "Image" without active image
Then I should see Asset Manager panel display
Then I should see image asset item with name "img1" display
Then I should see image asset item with name "img2" display
Then I should see image asset item list match with baseline title "WEB.JIT007.Asset.ListItem.Img1Img2" with threshold "1"
When I select image name "img1" in Asset Manager panel
Then I should see the preview web editor match with baseline title "WEB.JIT007.Asset.Img1" for the threshold "1"
When I select image name "img2" in Asset Manager panel
Then I should see the preview web editor match with baseline title "WEB.JIT007.Asset.Img2" for the threshold "1"
